<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id122554d7-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id122554d8-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2014—<ref href="/us/pl/113/235">Pub. L. 113–235</ref> substituted “Director of the Government Publishing Office” for “Public Printer”.</p>
</note>
